{"tid":1797401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：暴徒惡行令聖誕未能普天同慶","createTime":"2019-12-25T11:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T13:19:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"442a0a273b83a8616329cdaac7b3b179b2de4c2a","tid":1797401,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191225-14_znkIa_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191225-14_znkIa_1200x0.png&h=44421b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚（24日）平安夜，市民發起全港五區商場「和理 Shop」活動，與警方爆發衝突。特首林鄭月娥今日傍晚透過 Facebook 表示，人人都希望在平安夜歡度佳節，可惜「暴徒」又四出破壞，令市民大感無奈。林鄭月娥指，「暴徒」的惡行令今年聖誕佳節未能普天同慶，亦令稍微轉好的市道蒙上陰影。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥批評，「自私的暴徒在節日期間漫無目的地進行破壞，完全罔顧其他人的權利和自由」。林鄭月娥強調，政府必定全力遏止暴力，「令所有違法的人面對應得的後果」，務求回復社會正常生活及秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E6%83%A1%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A4%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%99%AE%E5%A4%A9%E5%90%8C%E6%85%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E6%2583%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2585%25B6%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=c4d6dc84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E6%2583%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2585%25B6%2F&h=c8ae3805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E6%83%A1%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A4%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%99%AE%E5%A4%A9%E5